{"tid":1612962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"代表律師：醫生稱印尼女記者右眼將永久失明 (19:39)","createTime":"2019-10-02T11:50:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T11:56:46.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"619d0c8c3a858a11fc204923e89d5dcb0a6637dd","tid":1612962,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"本地印尼語傳媒SUARA女記者Veby Mega Indah日前在灣仔站行人天橋採訪遊行時，疑被數米外的警員擎槍射中右眼眼眉，眼球沒有破裂。Indah的代表律師韋智達今晚（2日）表示，醫生經診治後告知，Indah的右眼將永久失明，其瞳孔因外力衝擊破裂，永久損傷程度有待Indah進行手術後才能評估。Indah的家人現時身在香港陪伴在側。<br />\n<br />\n韋智達稱，收到第三方證據顯示，射中Indah的是橡膠子彈而非布袋彈。"},{"pid":"fe4c651d433838fcc03991fef9d9aab7d73e2e29","tid":1612962,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:50:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">射中Indah的是橡膠子彈</span>"},{"pid":"c18c45e6a25e7bcff52c880d8bf195c7b224110c","tid":1612962,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5dcc97170f542f1e5ef262c1fa695f77ebf7e0","tid":1612962,"uid":160466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n推上國際！"},{"pid":"b450cd7166b0c228eb0293990f9447df3da32053","tid":1612962,"uid":253333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:53:10.000Z","msg":"Push!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"59c7afe610116a0ee5ecdb8de2ad13302fa8d41a","tid":1612962,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:53:19.000Z","msg":"支持印尼排華"},{"pid":"40470d5ce027ad77a5b47f22fd30da1831d38eb9","tid":1612962,"uid":163216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":